{"tid":263611,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"極度懷疑自己有齊晒抑鬱焦慮強迫恐懼症可以點做？","createTime":"2017-05-30T07:23:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-30T08:54:41.000Z","uid":30259,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d3f97021c9d82341ef4e5e79065a2c1585df63d2","tid":263611,"uid":30259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T07:23:19.000Z","msg":"完全未睇過醫生，係出面一直扮緊正常人，每日心理上都好辛苦過日子，覺得世界係灰色，日日都想死覺得自己係宇宙一粒塵都不如，有同屋企人講但佢地唔想我睇醫生，怕有左精神病紀錄會比社會D人標籤，同唔知點樣面對親戚，而且屋企人要靠我養我唔可以唔做野唔可以死，佢地叫我唔好諗咁多無謂野，靠自己自愈都唔好睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我真係改變唔到"},{"pid":"a8436101f142e8ff41ed6d0afbed77bcf456104d","tid":263611,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T07:24:58.000Z","msg":"邊鬼個知你有精神病紀錄咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88902a38f19017f90c8d2e820b4f43ef3de7f7af","tid":263611,"uid":110018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T07:25:14.000Z","msg":"睇醫生啦真心 唔好再比自己跌落去"},{"pid":"75aff90f30a4d7b1bdbfb5b612044affb1af427b","tid":263611,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T07:25:34.000Z","msg":"學屈原"},{"pid":"544f44b0f35f35d18cc3dd617e9510d19a2760ae","tid":263611,"uid":110018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T07:26:04.000Z","msg":"情緒病係要睇精神科食藥同做心理輔導 加油啊"},{"pid":"2b4f5b419ffee81ae3b7c45dd8f00e9950accc42","tid":263611,"uid":33821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T07:26:49.000Z","msg":"點會靠自己就好<br />\n仲信埋d無謂野 唔好比佢地累死 <br />\n去睇醫生啦"},{"pid":"8e0581c3574f294bb74788e1ca68dfc7c314e477","tid":263611,"uid":105911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T07:27:04.000Z","msg":"揀過另一份工啦"},{"pid":"126cd0d68a1d95b8f309a495accdade7652bd54f","tid":263611,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T07:27:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊鬼個知你有精神病紀錄咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cl